{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/features.png?t=1740492936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <strong>Experience </strong>a<strong> musical pacifist adventure</strong> much more focused on <strong>emotions</strong> and <strong>characters</strong> rather than fighting and action. (Beware of the &quot;friendly-looking angels&quot;, nonetheless!)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get to <strong>listen</strong> to a <strong>rich soundtrack</strong> and <strong>play exciting music-themed mini games</strong>, <strong>turn-based bosses</strong> and more! (Some of them are really challenging.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Travel the world</strong> and get to <strong>save it</strong> through an <strong>original story</strong> and <strong>deep lore</strong> with glimpses of <strong>humor</strong>! (I've heard the dads and moms' stories are neat...)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No one gets hurt</strong>. You'll have to use something <strong>other than violence</strong> in order to <strong>solve conflicts</strong>. (Maybe use your brain? Or your heart?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choices matter</strong>! Whenever a decision is presented to you, <strong>choose carefully</strong>! It may <strong>impact the story</strong> and how other <strong>characters feel about you</strong>. (It may also impact how you feel about yourself, huh.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Promote nature and animal protection everywhere</strong>. Even if you gotta <strong>fight for it</strong>! (*ahem* Fighting as defending it. Never forget about the fourth feature. NEVER.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can <strong>feed pigeons</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/Joy_thumbup.gif?t=1740492936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/inspiration.png?t=1740492936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore</strong>, talk to <strong>NPCs</strong> and <strong>find gems</strong> in overworld then <strong>trade</strong> them for delicious healthy snacks which you can later use to brighten your mood up during <strong>fights</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can also <strong>trade</strong> gems for <strong>gears</strong> that could provide nice <strong>advantage</strong> facing <strong>bosses</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Work your way into <strong>boss fights</strong> <strong>peacefully</strong> by using your <strong>words</strong>. You should be able to <strong>convince</strong> and <strong>change their mind</strong> if you choose the correct ones.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Some <strong>angels</strong> aren't much up for <strong>conversations</strong>! They will let you know by <strong>attacking</strong>. Don't get <strong>hit</strong> <strong>too much</strong> or you might run out of <strong>motivation</strong> to continue.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>MIP</strong> stands for <strong>Mind Points</strong> and <strong>MOP</strong> stands for <strong>Mood Points</strong>. These work like the <strong>HP</strong> of the <strong>player</strong> and the <strong>boss</strong>.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/the_heroes.png?t=1740492936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/teststeam.png?t=1740492936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/teststeam3.png?t=1740492936\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/teststeam2.png?t=1740492936\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3390520?t=1740492936","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740492936","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/72b0e24c92562b98f8054a4374c4fcee5409126c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740492936","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/72b0e24c92562b98f8054a4374c4fcee5409126c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740492936","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3395660,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3390520/extras/features.png?t=1740492936\" /></p><p 